---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="The terms of use for Honestly Profitable. Educational information only — not financial, legal, or investment advice. Use at your own risk and do your own research."
  path="/terms"
>
  <div class="container container-narrow page-head">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Terms' }]} />
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="lead">By using {SITE.name}, you agree to these terms.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container container-narrow page-body">
    <h2>Educational information only</h2>
    <p>
      All content on {SITE.name} is provided for general educational and informational purposes
      only. It is not financial, legal, investment, tax, or professional advice, and it is not a
      recommendation to start any particular business. Starting a business involves real financial
      risk. You are solely responsible for your own decisions and for doing your own research and
      seeking qualified professional advice before spending money.
    </p>

    <h2>No guarantees</h2>
    <p>
      Startup costs, earnings ranges, timelines, and difficulty assessments are informed estimates
      based on publicly reported data and operator accounts. They are not guarantees or predictions
      of your results. Individual outcomes vary significantly based on location, skill, effort,
      market conditions, regulation, and factors outside anyone's control. We make no warranty that
      any business will be profitable or suitable for you.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy and changes</h2>
    <p>
      We work to keep content accurate and current, but we do not warrant that it is complete,
      error-free, or up to date. Costs, regulations, and market conditions change. We may update,
      add, or remove content at any time without notice.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party links and advertising</h2>
    <p>
      The site may contain links to third-party websites and may display third-party advertising. We
      do not control and are not responsible for the content, products, or practices of any
      third-party sites or advertisers. Links and ads are not endorsements.
    </p>

    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>
      You agree not to misuse the site, including by attempting to disrupt it, scrape it at a scale
      that burdens our infrastructure, or republish substantial portions of our content without
      permission. Content on this site is owned by {SITE.name} or its licensors and is protected by
      applicable law.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, {SITE.name} and its operators are not liable for any
      loss or damage — including lost profits, lost capital, or business losses — arising from your
      use of, or reliance on, anything on this site. You use the site and act on its information
      entirely at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
    <p>We may revise these terms from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes means you accept the revised terms.</p>

    <p class="page-updated">Last updated: June 2026 · {SITE.domain}</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
